detectors.description:
Reentrancy in SmartRoulette.placeBet(uint256,bytes32,bytes32) ():
	External calls:
	- (affiliate,coef_affiliate,coef_player) = smartAffiliateContract.getAffiliateInfo(msg.sender) ()
	- (playerTokens,errorCodeEmission) = smartToken.emission(msg.sender,affiliate,msg.value,coef_player,coef_affiliate) ()
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- gambles.push(g) ()
	SmartRoulette.gambles () can be used in cross function reentrancies:
	- SmartRoulette.GetGameIndexesToProcess() ()
	- SmartRoulette.ProcessGame(uint256,uint256) ()
	- SmartRoulette.calcRandomNumberAndGetPreliminaryGameResult(uint256,uint64) ()
	- SmartRoulette.emergencyFixGameResult(uint64,uint256) ()
	- SmartRoulette.getGame(uint64) ()
	- SmartRoulette.placeBet(uint256,bytes32,bytes32) ()
	- SmartRoulette.preliminaryGameResult(uint64) ()
	- SmartRoulette.totalGames() ()
detectors.markdown:
Reentrancy in [SmartRoulette.placeBet(uint256,bytes32,bytes32)]():
	External calls:
	- [(affiliate,coef_affiliate,coef_player) = smartAffiliateContract.getAffiliateInfo(msg.sender)]()
	- [(playerTokens,errorCodeEmission) = smartToken.emission(msg.sender,affiliate,msg.value,coef_player,coef_affiliate)]()
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- [gambles.push(g)]()
	[SmartRoulette.gambles]() can be used in cross function reentrancies:
	- [SmartRoulette.GetGameIndexesToProcess()]()
	- [SmartRoulette.ProcessGame(uint256,uint256)]()
	- [SmartRoulette.calcRandomNumberAndGetPreliminaryGameResult(uint256,uint64)]()
	- [SmartRoulette.emergencyFixGameResult(uint64,uint256)]()
	- [SmartRoulette.getGame(uint64)]()
	- [SmartRoulette.placeBet(uint256,bytes32,bytes32)]()
	- [SmartRoulette.preliminaryGameResult(uint64)]()
	- [SmartRoulette.totalGames()]()
